Known Issues:

1)  OnLevelWasLoaded, OnLevelWasInitialized, OnUpdate, OnFixedUpdate, OnLateUpdate, OnGUI, and OnApplicationQuit only work in MUPOT Mode.
2)  MUPOT Mode does not work without Assembly generated.
3)  MUPOT Mode is not directing the Managed folder to the proper location.
4)  Mono Game Support is currently bugged for Unity 2017.4.28f1.  (Signature for PlayerLoadFirstScene in IL2CPPUnityPlayer.cpp and MonoUnityPlayer.cpp is returning NULL.)
5)  The Check for 64bit needs to be redone.

---

Work-in-Progress / To-Do List:

1)  Fix the above issues.
2)  Redesign the Log system to combine both Debug and Release Logs in one unified system.
3)  Create Method for ModPrefs to Register Categories and Prefs in a single call.
4)  An Assembly Generator for Game Specific Assembly DLLs.
5)  A Dependency Download system to automate installation of MelonLoader.
6)  A Unity Dependency Extractor for Unity Editor installations to streamline the process of getting Unity Dependencies.
7)  Add Assertion System.
8)  Add Android Support.
9)  Add Linux Support.
10)  Add Mac OS Support.

